STATE
v.
Antoine Denard YOUNG. No. 577P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 3, 2005. Constance E. Widenhouse, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Antoine Denard Young. Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th day of December 2004 by the Attorney General to Deem Response Timely Filed:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of March 2005."
